enum.name: DNBIAMfgAssemblyType
enum.abstract: This file defines the possible types of a Manufacturing Assembly.

class.name: MfgAssembly
class.abstract: This Interface represents a Manufacturing Assembly.

method.name: AddPart
method.abstract: Assignes a part (Product, Resource or other MA/MK) to the Manufacturing Assembly.

method.name: Item
method.abstract: Returns one assigned Part (Product, Resource or other MA/MK) of the Manufacturing Assembly.

method.name: RemovePart
method.abstract: Removes a part (Product, Resource or other MA/MK) from the Manufacturing Assembly.

method.name: MAName
method.abstract: Returns or sets the Name of the Manufacturing Assembly.

method.name: MAPartNumber
method.abstract: Returns or sets the Part Number of the Manufacturing Assembly.

method.name: MAType
method.abstract: Returns the Type of the Manufacturing Assembly.

class.name: MfgAssemblyFactory
class.abstract: Represents the factory to creates a manufacturing assembly.

method.name: CreateMfgAssembly
method.abstract: Creates a manufacturing assembly of given type "iType".

method.name: RemoveMfgAssembly
method.abstract: Removes a given Manufacturing Assembly from the MA Applicative Container.

method.name: RetrieveMfgAssembly
method.abstract: Retrieve all the Manufacturing Assemblies of a given name.

method.name: RetrieveMfgAssemblyAtIndex
method.abstract: Retrieves a Manufacturing Assembly at the given index from the MA Applicative Container.

method.name: RetriveALLMfgAssy
method.abstract: Retrieve all the Manufacturing Assemblies of a given type.
